snippet.title: Morbolbo: Enter the Maze Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.LaughingTower.Morbolbo_PC
Or on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1138310/Morbolbo_Enter_the_Maze/

Morbolbo: Enter the Maze is a puzzle/adventure game where you have to navigate a maze full of traps and collect as much treasure as possible. Take control of Morbolbo - the musketeer, as he goes on adventures into mazes and labyrinths, avoiding dangerous traps and fighting leprechauns that guard the treasures.
